                                           name='admin_0_countries',
                                           scale='50m',
                                           facecolor='none',
                                           edgecolor='black',
                                           linewidth=0.1))
# plot figure and colorbar
cf = ax.contourf(ds.lon,ds.lat,ds.prec.mean(dim='time'),cmap='Blues',levels=np.arange(0,0.4,.05),extend='both')
cbar = plt.colorbar(cf,shrink=.5)

# Add gridlines 
gl = ax.gridlines(crs=ccrs.PlateCarree(), linewidth=0.1, color='black', alpha=1)
# masks or feature
ax.add_feature(cfeature.OCEAN, facecolor='lightskyblue',zorder=1)
ax.add_feature(cfeature.COASTLINE,linewidth=0.5,zorder=2)
# x label and tick
ax.set_xticks(np.linspace(70, 140, 8))
ax.set_xlabel('LONGITUDE',fontsize=10)
# y label and tick

ax.set_ylabel('LATITUDE',fontsize=10)
# annotate

             bbox=dict(boxstyle='round,pad=0.5', fc='white', ec='black',lw=0.5 ,alpha=0.5))

      #2.2 在2.1的基础上进行区域选择作图
#project
plt.figure(figsize=(11,11),dpi=100)
ax = plt.axes(projection=ccrs.PlateCarree())
proj=ccrs.PlateCarree()
ax.add_feature(cfeature.NaturalEarthFeature(category='cultural',
                                           name='admin_0_countries',
                                           scale='50m',
                                           facecolor='none',
                                           edgecolor='black',
                                           linewidth=0.1))

# plot figure and colorbar
cf = ax.contourf(ds.lon,ds.lat,ds.prec.mean(dim='time'),cmap='Blues',levels=np.arange(0,0.4,.01),extend='both')#extend加小尖尖
cbar = plt.colorbar(cf,shrink=.5)

# Add gridlines
ax.gridlines(draw_labels=True)
ax.set_extent([100,130,20,30])

# masks or feature
ax.add_feature(cfeature.OCEAN, facecolor='lightskyblue',zorder=1)
ax.add_feature(cfeature.COASTLINE,linewidth=0.5,zorder=2)

# x label and tick
#ax.set_xticks(np.linspace(100, 130, 5))在区域选取“ax.set_extent([100,130,20,30])”这一步已有x和y轴tick
ax.set_xlabel('LONGITUDE',fontsize=10)

# y label and tick
#ax.set_yticks(np.linspace(20,30, 4))在区域选取“ax.set_extent([100,130,20,30])”这一步已有x和y轴tick
ax.set_ylabel('LATITUDE',fontsize=10)

# annotate
ax.annotate('Shenzhen',xy=(114,23),xytext=(115,24),fontsize=8,arrowprops=dict(lw=0.5,color='k'),
             bbox=dict(boxstyle='round,pad=0.5', fc='white', ec='black',lw=0.5 ,alpha=0.5))
# legend
ax.scatter(121.5,25,s=50,c='r',marker='*',label='Taibei',edgecolors='k', linewidths=0.5)
ax.legend(loc='lower right',fontsize=12)

# text box
ax.text(110,27,'In Taiwan Province,\nthe precipitation rate in the south Taiwan is greater than that in the north.',
         fontsize=8,bbox=dict(boxstyle='round,pad=0.3', fc='white', ec='black',lw=0.5 ,alpha=0.7))

# title
ax.set_title("Southeast China daily mean precipitation rate of 2018 (%)")
